@page "/docs/transitions"

<PageTitle>Transitions — BlazorMotion</PageTitle>

<div class="breadcrumb">Docs / <span>Transitions</span></div>
<h1>Transitions</h1>
<p>A <code>TransitionConfig</code> controls <em>how</em> a value animates from its current state to the target — duration, easing, type, and delay.</p>

<h2>Animation types</h2>

<h3>Tween</h3>
<p>Duration-based animation with an easing curve. The default type.</p>
<pre><code>new TransitionConfig
{
    Type     = "tween",
    Duration = 0.3,
    Ease     = "easeInOut"
}</code></pre>

<h3>Spring</h3>
<p>Physics-based spring animation. Use for natural, responsive feel.</p>
<pre><code>new TransitionConfig
{
    Type      = "spring",
    Stiffness = 200,
    Damping   = 20,
    Mass      = 1
}</code></pre>

<h3>BounceSpring (Framer-compatible)</h3>
<p>Visual-duration spring using <code>bounce</code> (0 = no bounce, 1 = very bouncy):</p>
<pre><code>// Static factory
TransitionConfig.BounceSpring(duration: 0.5, bounce: 0.25, mass: 1)
</code></pre>

<div class="demo-area" style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <Motion Class="demo-box"
            Initial="@(new AnimationProps { X = -60 })"
            Animate="@(new AnimationProps { X = 60 })"
            Transition="@(new TransitionConfig { Type = TransitionType.Tween, Duration = 0.5, Ease = BlazorMotion.Models.Easing.EaseInOut })">
        Tween
    </Motion>
    <Motion Class="demo-box"
            Initial="@(new AnimationProps { X = -60 })"
            Animate="@(new AnimationProps { X = 60 })"
            Transition="@(new TransitionConfig { Type = TransitionType.Spring, Stiffness = 300, Damping = 10 })">
        Spring
    </Motion>
    <Motion Class="demo-box"
            Initial="@(new AnimationProps { X = -60 })"
            Animate="@(new AnimationProps { X = 60 })"
            Transition="@(TransitionConfig.BounceSpring(0.6, 0.4))">
        Bounce
    </Motion>
</div>

<h3>Inertia</h3>
<p>Momentum-based deceleration primarily used after drag gestures:</p>
<pre><code>new TransitionConfig
{
    Type          = "inertia",
    Velocity      = 500,
    TimeConstant  = 750,
    Min           = 0,
    Max           = 1000
}</code></pre>

<h3>Keyframes</h3>
<p>Animate through a sequence of values:</p>
<pre><code>new TransitionConfig
{
    Type     = "keyframes",
    Values   = new[] { 0.0, 1.2, 0.9, 1.0 },
    Times    = new[] { 0.0, 0.6, 0.8, 1.0 },
    Duration = 0.8
}</code></pre>

<h2>TransitionConfig reference</h2>
<table class="prop-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td>Type</td><td>string?</td><td>"tween"</td><td>"tween" | "spring" | "inertia" | "keyframes"</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Duration</td><td>double?</td><td>0.3</td><td>Animation duration in seconds (tween/keyframes)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Ease</td><td>string?</td><td>"easeOut"</td><td>Easing name or cubic-bezier string</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Delay</td><td>double?</td><td>0</td><td>Delay before animation starts (seconds)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Repeat</td><td>int?</td><td>0</td><td>Number of repetitions (int.MaxValue for infinite)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>RepeatType</td><td>string?</td><td>"loop"</td><td>"loop" | "reverse" | "mirror"</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Stiffness</td><td>double?</td><td>100</td><td>Spring stiffness (spring type)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Damping</td><td>double?</td><td>10</td><td>Spring damping (spring type)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Mass</td><td>double?</td><td>1</td><td>Spring mass (spring type)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Bounce</td><td>double?</td><td>—</td><td>0–1 bounce amount (BounceSpring)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>VisualDuration</td><td>double?</td><td>—</td><td>Perceived duration in seconds (BounceSpring)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Velocity</td><td>double?</td><td>0</td><td>Initial velocity (inertia/spring)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>TimeConstant</td><td>double?</td><td>750</td><td>Deceleration constant ms (inertia)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>OnUpdate</td><td>Action&lt;double&gt;?</td><td>—</td><td>Called each frame with current value</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h2>Easing functions</h2>
<pre><code>"linear" | "easeIn" | "easeOut" | "easeInOut"
"circIn" | "circOut" | "circInOut"
"backIn" | "backOut" | "backInOut"
"anticipate"
"[0.17, 0.67, 0.83, 0.67]"   // custom cubic-bezier</code></pre>
